<% p = asset.is_a?(Pseudonym) ? asset : asset.pseudonym %>

<% define_content :link do %>
  <%= HostUrl.context_host(asset.account) %>
<% end %>

<% define_content :subject do %>
  <%= t :subject, "HotChalk Ember Account Created" %>
<% end %>

<%= t :body, "Dear %{name},", :name => p.user.name %>

Welcome to the HotChalk Ember Learning Management System (LMS) platform.

To access HotChalk Ember:

   • Login to <%= content :link %> with your username and password. Please bookmark this page, if you have not done so already, as it is the only access point for your HotChalk Ember courses.

   • To view your courses, hover over the Courses tab at the top of the page. You will see all courses you are enrolled in that have been published.

   • If you are unable to access HotChalk Ember or your course, please submit a help ticket at https://support.hotchalkember.com/hc/en-us and our support team will get back to you promptly.

Warm regards,
HotChalk Ember Support